snippet.title: I AM DOG - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
I AM DOG is a 2D Vertical Scrolling Platformer, where you play as DOG chomping, stomping and bombing your way to the bottom to rescue your friends.

RELEASING NOVEMBER 19, 2024 ON STEAM AND ITCHIO

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2882280/I_AM_DOG/

https://fun-sewer-level.itch.io/i-am-dog
